<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindcss/browser@4"></script>
    <title>{% block title %}{% endblock %}</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="bg-gray-100 min-h-screen py-8">
        <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md">
            <div class="mb-8">
                <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">{% block header %}{% endblock %}</h1>
                <div class="h-1 w-20 bg-blue-500"></div>
            </div>

            <div class="prose prose-blue max-w-none">
                {% block content %}{% endblock %}
            </div>

            <div class="mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-gray-200 text-sm text-gray-600">
                <p>To jest automatyczna wiadomość, prosimy na nią nie odpowiadać.</p>
                <p class="mt-2">© {{ "now"|date("Y") }} System Zgłoszeń. Wszystkie prawa zastrzeżone.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 